Interface Permission.OnRequestPermissionsResult

    public static interface Permission.OnRequestPermissionsResult
    Provides callbacks for Permission#requestPermissionsFromRemote.

    • Method Detail

      • onResult

        void onResult​(String nodeId,
              String[] permissions,
              int[] grantResults)
        Called when the user agrees or rejects to grant requested permissions. This callback is invoked after Permission#requestPermissionsFromRemote is called.
        Parameters:
        nodeId - Indicates the network ID set in Permission#requestPermissionsFromRemote.
        permissions - Indicates the list of requested permissions set in Permission#requestPermissionsFromRemote.
        grantResults - Indicates the permission grant result. If the user agrees to grant the requested permissions, the value is 0; if the user rejects to grant the requested permissions, the value is -1.
        Since:
        4
        See Also:
        Permission.requestPermissionsFromRemote(String[], OnRequestPermissionsResult, String, String, int)

        permissions - Indicates the list of requested permissions set in Permission#requestPermissionsFromRemote.
